### Basic usage.


The most simple usage is generate a single file from a single `.bud` file.

Here is an example:

**.who-likes-what.txt.bud** (bud file)
```javascript
{{{read '../examples/01-minimum-demo/.who-likes-what.txt.bud'}}}
